    Verify your email so we can connect you to your bikes
  %h3.padded
    We sent an email to 
    %strong.stolen-color
      = @user.email
    with a confirmation link in it.
    %br
    Click the link in the email to finish signing up.
  .signup-image
    = image_tag "girl-with-bike.png", alt: "All signed up now, y'hear?"
